              Stearns Brakes Set the Standard for Excellence
Welcome to Southern Power, the southeast's leading 

            supplier of industrial electronics. Southern Power specializes in 

            motion control and automation. Among the advanced products we offer 

            from leading vendors are Stearns Brakes. 


            Stearns Brakes offers the most comprehensive line of spring-set disc 

            brakes on the market today. They have earned the reputation as the 

            industry's quality leader by working closely with their customers, 

            understanding their product needs, and developing products with the 

            design features to handle the most challenging applications. 


            Stearns has installed millions of disc brakes worldwide since 1935. 

            Many Stearns Brakes in service today are 40 years old or more; evidence 

            of product quality and reliability. 
